ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Metric States, Spaces, and Syntaxes introduces several recently developed tools for analyzing meter, including ski-hill graphs and beat-class sets. I would recommend the course for any theory student, because it addresses musical parameters and repertoires that receive limited attention in many other courses.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This course deepened my knowledge by addressing important and undervalued topics in my field. Indeed, I am particularly interested in metric theory, and will almost certainly rely on material from this course in my future research.
